Ill grab an example of a method that uses that in one of my servers.
Here is the void

    public void deletethatwall(int objectX, int objectY) {
        ReplaceObject2(objectX, objectY, 6951, -1, 0);
    }

Here is the method that uses it.

public void Deletewalls() { deletethatwall(ObjectX, ObjectY); }
